    <string name="burnout_score_info_title">How is the score calculated?</string>
    <string name="burnout_score_info_message">
    This score summarizes your level of digital fatigue based on your smartphone usage.\n\n
    It is calculated using five aspects:\n
    • Screen time\n
    • Usage fragmentation\n
    • Night usage\n
    • Notifications\n
    • Recent changes in your habits\n\n

    Each aspect is evaluated as low, medium, or high risk by comparing it to your usual usage.\n\n

    They are then combined to produce a final score between 0 and 2:\n\n

    0–0.7 → Low risk\n
    0.7–1.3 → Moderate risk\n
    >1.3 → High risk\n\n

    A higher value indicates a higher risk of digital burnout.
    </string>

